rap;\">user代码</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">public class User { &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; private String name; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; private Integer age; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; private Boolean isMarried; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; private Double income; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; private String[] interests; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; public String getName() { &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return name; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; } &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; public void setName(String name) { &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; this.name = name; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; } &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; public Integer getAge() { &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return age; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; } &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; public void setAge(Integer age) { &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; this.age = age; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; } &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; public Boolean getIsMarried() { &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return isMarried; &nbsp;